\muC_{\Psi}\left(i\right)=\cardp{\fnorm{\ip{i}{\Psi}}}{\fnorm{\ket{\Psi}}}=\cardp{\fnorm{\alpha_{i}}}{\fnorm{\ket{\Psi}}}\,,\label{eq:cardinalProbability}
